| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2023-2495 — Recovery Inhibition (lockbit3)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 78af01c8-6df6-5c3b-a108-99dfcfc25f42"
